[38;5;234mA [0m[38;5;234;3mQuickonf[0m[38;5;234m configuration file is composed of multiple sections, called groups. The group name starts at the beginning of the line, instructions are indented.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          [0m
[38;5;234m                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                       [0m
[38;5;235m[0m[38;5;234m  [0m[38;5;235mgroup name[38;5;234m [0m[38;5;234m                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          [0m
[0m[38;5;234m  [0m[38;5;235m  instruction A[38;5;234m [0m[38;5;234m                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                     [0m
[0m[38;5;234m  [0m[38;5;235m  instruction B[38;5;234m [0m[38;5;234m                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                     [0m
[0m[38;5;234m  [0m[38;5;235m  ...[38;5;234m [0m[38;5;234m                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                               [0m
[0m[38;5;234m  [0m[38;5;235m  instruction G[38;5;234m [0m[38;5;234m                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                     [0m
[0m[38;5;234m  [0m[38;5;235m    instruction H depending on instruction G[38;5;234m [0m[38;5;234m                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        [0m
[0m[38;5;234m  [0m[38;5;235m    instruction I depending on instruction G[38;5;234m [0m[38;5;234m                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        [0m
[0m[38;5;234m                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                       [0m
[38;5;234mIndentations length and type (spaces or tabs) is not strict, you may use whichever you want. Keep in mind that, when mixing indentations, tabs are considered to be equivalent to aligning to multiples of 8 spaces (ie. [0m[38;5;203;48;5;254m <space><space><tab> [0m[38;5;234m is equivalent to 8 spaces).                                                                                                                                                             [0m
[38;5;234m                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                       [0m
[38;5;234mSome instructions have an impact on multiple other instructions, like conditional execution ([0m[38;5;203;48;5;254m if [0m[38;5;234m) or repetition ([0m[38;5;203;48;5;254m repeat [0m[38;5;234m), in this case you must use a 2nd indentation level (or even more). See below for examples.                                                                                                                                                                                                                 [0m
[38;5;234m[38;5;234m [0m[38;5;234m                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      [0m
[0m[38;5;228;48;5;63;1m Commands [0m[38;5;234m[38;5;234m [0m[38;5;234m                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            [0m
[0m[38;5;234m                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                       [0m
[38;5;234mThe most important type of instruction is the commands. There are many available commands, and probably many more to come. A command is the instruction given to [0m[38;5;234;3mQuickonf[0m[38;5;234m for system checking and modification. The commands may need arguments and may return output values (see [0m[38;5;234;3mVariables[0m[38;5;234m below). See the [0m[38;5;234;3mCommands[0m[38;5;234m section for details on how to use commands.                                                                       [0m
[38;5;234m                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                       [0m
[38;5;234mBy convention, commands modifying data only for one user are prefixed with "[0m[38;5;203;48;5;254m user. [0m[38;5;234m" and take the username as their first argument. Other commands modify system-wide values.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          [0m
[38;5;234m[38;5;234m [0m[38;5;234m                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      [0m
[0m[38;5;228;48;5;63;1m Variables [0m[38;5;234m[38;5;234m [0m[38;5;234m                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                           [0m
[0m[38;5;234m                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                       [0m
[38;5;234mSome commands return output values, that can be stored in variables if needed. Variables are named with alphanumerical characters. Syntax to store values is the following:                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            [0m
[38;5;234m                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                       [0m
[38;5;235m[0m[38;5;234m  [0m[38;5;235mgroup name[38;5;234m [0m[38;5;234m                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          [0m
[0m[38;5;234m  [0m[38;5;235m  var1 var2 = command arg1 arg2[38;5;234m [0m[38;5;234m                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                     [0m
[0m[38;5;234m                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                       [0m
[38;5;234mUsing variables after assignment is as simple as putting the variable name between "<" and ">" anywhere, like:                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                         [0m
[38;5;234m                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                       [0m
[38;5;235m[0m[38;5;234m  [0m[38;5;235mgroup name[38;5;234m [0m[38;5;234m                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          [0m
[0m[38;5;234m  [0m[38;5;235m  var = command1 arg1 arg2[38;5;234m [0m[38;5;234m                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          [0m
[0m[38;5;234m  [0m[38;5;235m  command2 <var>[38;5;234m [0m[38;5;234m                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    [0m
[0m[38;5;234m                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                       [0m
[38;5;234m... here, the first output of the first command is used as the argument of the second command.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                         [0m
[38;5;234m[38;5;234m [0m[38;5;234m                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      [0m
[0m[38;5;27;1m## Global variables[0m[38;5;234m[38;5;234m [0m[38;5;234m                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                   [0m
[0m[38;5;234m                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                       [0m
[38;5;234mSome global variables are set when [0m[38;5;234;3mQuickonf[0m[38;5;234m starts:                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    [0m
[38;5;234m                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                       [0m
[38;5;234mâ€¢ [0m[38;5;203;48;5;254m hostname [0m[38;5;234m: the hostname of the computer                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                             [0m
[38;5;234mâ€¢ [0m[38;5;203;48;5;254m oscodename [0m[38;5;234m: the codename of the current operating system version                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                   [0m
[38;5;234mâ€¢ [0m[38;5;203;48;5;254m confdir [0m[38;5;234m: path of the directory containing the configuration file (can be used to read other files in the same directory, templates etc)                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            [0m
[38;5;234m[38;5;234m [0m[38;5;234m                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      [0m
[0m[38;5;27;1m## Expanding variables content[0m[38;5;234m[38;5;234m [0m[38;5;234m                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        [0m
[0m[38;5;234m                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                       [0m
[38;5;234mSometimes, a variable's content refers to other variables. Take for instance a file that contains variables names. If you read the file with the [0m[38;5;203;48;5;254m file.read [0m[38;5;234m command, it may be stored in a variable, but the content of the read file is not processed for variables names. In order to process variables names references inside a variable content, simply use the [0m[38;5;203;48;5;254m expand [0m[38;5;234m instruction with the variable name as its only argument.[0m
[38;5;234m                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                       [0m
[38;5;234mExample:                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                               [0m
[38;5;234m                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                       [0m
[38;5;235m[0m[38;5;234m  [0m[38;5;235mAPT sources[38;5;234m [0m[38;5;234m                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                         [0m
[0m[38;5;234m  [0m[38;5;235m  aptsrc = file.read <confdir>/sources.list.tmpl[38;5;234m [0m[38;5;234m                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    [0m
[0m[38;5;234m  [0m[38;5;235m  expand aptsrc[38;5;234m [0m[38;5;234m                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                     [0m
[0m[38;5;234m  [0m[38;5;235m  file.content /etc/apt/sources.list <aptsrc>[38;5;234m [0m[38;5;234m                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                       [0m
[0m[38;5;234m                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                       [0m
[38;5;234m... here, the [0m[38;5;203;48;5;254m sources.list.tmpl [0m[38;5;234m file may contain [0m[38;5;203;48;5;254m <oscodename> [0m[38;5;234m.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                     [0m
[38;5;234m[38;5;234m [0m[38;5;234m                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      [0m
[0m[38;5;228;48;5;63;1m Conditional execution [0m[38;5;234m[38;5;234m [0m[38;5;234m                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                               [0m
[0m[38;5;234m                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                       [0m
[38;5;234mInstructions can be grouped below a [0m[38;5;203;48;5;254m if [0m[38;5;234m instruction, which executes then only if the condition is true.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                               [0m
[38;5;234m                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                       [0m
[38;5;234mSupported conditions are:                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              [0m
[38;5;234m                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                       [0m
[38;5;234mâ€¢ [0m[38;5;203;48;5;254m file.absent </path/to/file> [0m[38;5;234m: true if the file does not exist                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                       [0m
[38;5;234mâ€¢ [0m[38;5;203;48;5;254m file.present </path/to/file> [0m[38;5;234m: true if the file exists                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              [0m
[38;5;234mâ€¢ [0m[38;5;203;48;5;254m <value1> = <value2> [0m[38;5;234m: true if values are equal (compared as strings)                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                [0m
[38;5;234mâ€¢ [0m[38;5;203;48;5;254m <value1> != <value2> [0m[38;5;234m: true if values are different (compared as strings)                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                           [0m
[38;5;234m                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                       [0m
[38;5;234mExample:                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                               [0m
[38;5;234m                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                       [0m
[38;5;235m[0m[38;5;234m  [0m[38;5;235mVPN[38;5;234m [0m[38;5;234m                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                 [0m
[0m[38;5;234m  [0m[38;5;235m  if <hostname> = mylaptop[38;5;234m [0m[38;5;234m                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          [0m
[0m[38;5;234m  [0m[38;5;235m    nm.import openvpn <confdir>/myvpn.ovpn[38;5;234m [0m[38;5;234m                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          [0m
[0m[38;5;234m                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                       [0m
[38;5;234m... here, the [0m[38;5;203;48;5;254m nm.import openvpn <confdir>/myvpn.ovpn [0m[38;5;234m is only executed if the host name is "mylaptop". You may of course put multiple instructions with the 2nd indentation level.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    [0m
