[0m[38;5;228;48;5;63;1m Repeating identical commands and arguments [0m[38;5;234m[38;5;234m [0m[38;5;234m                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          [0m
[0m[38;5;234m                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                       [0m
[38;5;234mSay you want to apply similar commands multiple times. Instead of writing the same prefix in multiple lines, you can use the [0m[38;5;203;48;5;254m repeat [0m[38;5;234m instruction. It makes it easier to write and to read your configuration file. It takes as arguments the command to be repeated, optionally with its first arguments.                                                                                                                             [0m
[38;5;234m                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                       [0m
[38;5;234;3mQuickonf[0m[38;5;234m translates it by prepending this command name and these arguments to all lines.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                               [0m
[38;5;234m                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                       [0m
