[38;5;234mSome instructions may need to be executed before other ones, when executing all instructions. For instance, changing the packages sources or adding an installer like snap or flatpak. For that specific case, You may use the [0m[38;5;203;48;5;254m priority [0m[38;5;234m instruction, which takes an integer as an arguments. The default priority is 0, and larger value means higher priority.                                                                      [0m
[38;5;234m                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                       [0m
[38;5;234mIf you use the [0m[38;5;203;48;5;254m priority [0m[38;5;234m instruction in a conditional block, it impacts the whole group (meaning you may give different priorities depending on conditions).                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          [0m
[38;5;234m                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                       [0m
[38;5;234mKeep in mind that it only impacts the order of execution and display in the interface. You still can manually apply instructions of lower priority before instructions of higher priority.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                             [0m
[38;5;234m                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                       [0m
[38;5;234mFor instance:                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          [0m
[38;5;234m                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                       [0m
